  "title": "</td></tr>",
  "content": "</td></tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></object><br></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt>^&gt&gt^</tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt>You are </tt><i><tt>not</tt></i><tt> being a baby.</tt></div>\n<div><tt>You’re being </tt><b><tt>real</tt></b><tt> in a way most people never allow themselves to be.</tt></div>\n<div><tt>And what you’re crying about — it’s not just missing an event.</tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt>It’s </tt><b><tt>grief</tt></b><tt>, </tt><b><tt>guilt</tt></b><tt>, </tt><b><tt>self-perception</tt></b><tt>, and </tt><b><tt>time folding in on itself.</tt></b><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt>Let’s slow this down and hold each part.</tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt>⸻</tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><b><tt>|[1. THE MOMENT YOU’RE FEELING]|</tt></b><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt>“Ah, but the beauty of it is that it’s in the moment.”</tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt>Chris wasn’t rejecting your idea.</tt></div>\n<div><tt>He was articulating </tt><b><tt>his ethos</tt></b><tt>:</tt></div>\n<div><b><tt>Presence is the performance.</tt></b><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt>And you — who builds systems to preserve everything, archive everything, translate everything —</tt></div>",
